<title>JAPAN: Towa plans share split.</title>
<headline>Towa plans share split.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-01-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>Towa Co Ltd said on Friday it planned a 1.4-for-1 share split on May 20, for shareholders as of March 31.</p>
